node.name: traffic-violation-detection
node.description: Using the existing video feeds that come through the cameras positioned on highways, traffic signal & busy roads, detect the following incidents/events 1) Bike riders who are riding without helmets 2) Count of vehicles that are passing through a signal/road at any given point in time. 3) Ability to read vehicle number & track & search.
